        "gg2ZlfZeBiP_text": "See Visible Changes&nbsp;<br>in 3-4 Weeks",
        "ggBrJW3x9zy_text": "<p>Berberine enhances your metabolism, helping your body <strong>burn fat </strong>more efficiently.</p>",
        "ggFBlGW9qgN_text": "<p>Apple cider vinegar capsules <strong>reduce bloating</strong> and improve digestion, giving you a more comfortable and lighter feeling.</p>",
        "ggLIrbg8574_text": "<p>30 day money back guarantee</p>",
        "ggNNJLlZfP2_text": "<p>Saffron extract helps reduce cravings and <strong>emotional eating</strong>, making it easier to stick to your healthy eating plan.</p>",
        "ggNkPdTcwct_text": "Craving Control",
        "ggQzqdhQn6D_text": "Improved Digestion",
        "ggbXHlTuwAI_text": "Metabolism Boost",
        "ggi_rFyWctl_label": "REVEAL OFFER",
        "ggmj4rbaVQk_text": "<p>Achieving your weight loss goals has never been easier. With our Weight Management Bundle, you can start seeing and <strong>feeling</strong> the difference in just a few short weeks. This powerful combination of saffron extract, berberine, and apple cider vinegar capsules works synergistically to help you shed those extra pounds that you never wanted to put on.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-521646304179258226"
    },
    "gp_section_521646304649020355": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "3f2c19aa28df6f39e52269fb11a8d8b05c1c7372006e9b5363710148d033b595_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg6HRqhC-kR_text": "<p>Saffron extract reduces cravings and emotional eating, making it easier to stick to your healthy eating plan.</p>",
        "gg6YsuF2EIW_text": "Enhance Your Energy",
        "ggCTfAqBUGs_text": "Control Your Cravings",
        "ggFTav58F5C_text": "<p>Apple cider vinegar capsules reduce bloating and improve digestion, helping you feel lighter and more comfortable.</p>",
        "ggFl0YynnV9_text": "<p>Feel more energized throughout the day, making it easier to stay active and motivated on your weight loss journey.</p><p>Take the first step towards a healthier, happier you with our Weight Management Bundle!</p>",
        "ggNPKra5RFi_text": "Improve Your Digestion",
        "ggNti8QE6_b_text": "Transform Your Body with Our Weight Management Bundle",
        "ggZ4r4UN5Kk_text": "<p>Struggling with weight loss? Your favorite jeans not fitting? Tired of carrying those extra 15 pounds? Our Weight Management Bundle is here to help you have the body you’ve always wanted.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-521646304649020355"
    },
    "gp_section_521646307383706693": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "b6877a85c4190a762e2cca7fae614d4d0c932529e6180d95296435d2c0c3371e_1_1_0_0__1",
        "ggBxQuA0TTw_label": "REVEAL OFFER",
        "ggJ9gpAXWQe_text": "<p>Our Weight Management Bundle is formulated with natural ingredients that are generally well-tolerated. Some people might experience mild digestive changes as their body adjusts, but these are usually temporary. Always consult your healthcare provider before starting any new supplement regimen.</p>",
        "ggKhMH70q1y_childItem_0": "<p>How soon will I start seeing results with the Weight Management Bundle?</p>",
        "ggKhMH70q1y_childItem_1": "<p>Are there any side effects to using saffron extract, berberine, or apple cider vinegar capsules?</p>",
        "ggKhMH70q1y_childItem_2": "<p>How do these supplements help with weight loss?</p>",
        "ggKhMH70q1y_childItem_3": "<p>Can I take these supplements if I’m already on medication?</p>",
        "ggROcswfaEj_text": "<p>While our supplements are natural, it’s important to consult with your healthcare provider before starting any new supplements, especially if you are taking medication or have any underlying health conditions.</p>",
        "ggY_K9cG027_text": "<p>30 day money back guarantee</p>",
        "ggfPCNjVY7t_text": "<p>Frequently Asked Questions</p>",
        "ggn9vsU_t8v_text": "<p>Many of our customers start noticing reduced cravings and improved digestion within the first week. Visible changes in weight and energy levels typically become noticeable within 3-4 weeks with consistent use.</p>",
        "ggr1fYveG_v_text": "<p>Need help finding an answer to your question? Ask our customer support at <strong>info@ancientbliss.com.</strong></p>",
        "ggy6Ia3HhZx_text": "<p>Saffron extract helps control cravings, making it easier to stick to a healthy diet. Berberine boosts your metabolism, aiding in fat burning. Apple cider vinegar improves digestion and reduces bloating, helping you feel lighter and more comfortable.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-521646307383706693"
    },
